{"tid":981298,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"波蘭擬禁公共機構使用華為產品","createTime":"2019-01-14T07:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T10:56:33.000Z","uid":13468,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab49c713362942de8c409d7362859066a53801a","tid":981298,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T07:59:05.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】波蘭可能考慮禁止公共機構使用華為產品。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭政府一名負責網絡安全的官員透露，在拘捕華為波蘭分公司高層王偉晶後，當局無突然改變對華為的政策，但會研究公共機構使用華為產品的情況，考慮禁止它們使用華為產品。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，波蘭目前沒有法律手段強迫私人企業或公民停用任何一間科技公司的產品，政府可能會考慮收緊法例，限制可能威脅國家安全的科技產品流通。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭上周二拘捕王偉晶，指他為中國做間諜，華為隨後宣布終止跟王偉晶的僱傭關係。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭內政部則呼籲，歐盟及北約應就是否把華為剔出歐洲市場統一立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=334077&amp;fbclid=IwAR1SlmM7PJJIPkLlC4WGSZC576tGBZLlgOo1Kg3sQH7VVkXWC9ipxJaAufQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D334077%26fbclid%3DIwAR1SlmM7PJJIPkLlC4WGSZC576tGBZLlgOo1Kg3sQH7VVkXWC9ipxJaAufQ&d=LAkC%2Fxj5WDMblhR9Z6BKdkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=33954393\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D334077%26fbclid%3DIwAR1SlmM7PJJIPkLlC4WGSZC576tGBZLlgOo1Kg3sQH7VVkXWC9ipxJaAufQ&h=2acd07f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=334077&amp;fbclid=IwAR1SlmM7PJJIPkLlC4WGSZC576tGBZLlgOo1Kg3sQH7VVkXWC9ipxJaAufQ</a>"},{"pid":"11bd88e28b2f01294914167c146c96c2cf444a7c","tid":981298,"uid":202139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:10:50.000Z","msg":"又話間諜係個人行為，唔關華為事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又考慮禁止公共機構使用華為產品？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8469b4326b6558d9cc555926f5a53438602c65cd","tid":981298,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"